&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1977 indian kannada mythological film directed by hunsur krishnamurthy starring rajkumar in a dual role . the supporting cast features b. saroja devi , kanchana , jayamala , vajramuni , thoogudeepa srinivas and ramakrishna . the movie is based on one of the mahabharata character &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film won two awards at the 1976 – 77 karnataka state film awards — best actor ( rajkumar ) and best sound recording ( s. p. ramanathan ) .